 hall please enter up the steps and take the elevator to the third floor go right out of the elevator and aparc's receptionist will direct you please note that parking is monitored monday friday 8 am 4 pm traveling highway 280 north & south exit sand hill road east toward stanford continue east turning right at the traffic light on santa cruz avenue make an immediate left onto junipero serra boulevard turn left at the second stoplight campus drive east continue around campus drive east and turn left when you reach serra street follow serra street until it ends at galvez street turn right onto galvez and look for the first parking lot on the left which is a public pay parking lot upon walking out of the parking lot and turning to your right you will see encina hall encina hall is a four story stone building there are parking meters in front of the building aparc is on the third floor of the east wing of encina hall please enter up the steps and take the elevator to the third floor go right out of the elevator and aparc's receptionist will direct you please note that parking is monitored monday friday 8 am 4 pm additional parking there is additional parking along galvez street next to the stanford track stadium and next to the landau center galvez at memorial way contact voice 650 723 9741 fax 650 723 6530 search aparc search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages campus map printable map of the stanford campus 2.9 mb with parking areas indicated marguerite bus map the marguerite is stanford university's campus shuttle a printable map of the bus routes serving the stanford campus 700kb support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 9741 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
